Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.52,0:00:03.00,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}From a different point of view,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.00,0:00:04.88,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}even an imposing wall blocking\Nyour path is just a large door.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.88,0:00:06.26,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's a brand-new\Nsummer special!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.26,0:00:09.38,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A wedding with lots of police detectives,\Nand a culprit planning the perfect crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.38,0:00:10.88,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth\Nfor what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.88,0:00:12.68,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid\Nbut has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.68,0:00:14.70,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name?\NDetective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.26,0:02:05.27,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:10.06,Flashback Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Finally...\NFinally this day has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:13.27,Flashback Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I have conquered\Na legion of rivals,{needs a major edit. double XTL}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.27,0:02:16.69,Flashback Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and will finally vow\Nmy eternal future to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:35.46,Flashback Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}S-Sato{\rHonorifics - Flashback Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:47.10,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Takagi{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-kun{\r\be10}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:48.82,Flashback Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Y-Yumi{\rHonorifics - Flashback Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.82,0:02:50.44,Flashback Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yumi{\rHonorifics - Flashback Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.39,0:02:53.94,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ta-ka-gi{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-kun{\r\be10}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:59.03,Flashback Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}N-No... I wasn't...\NI wasn't supposed to marry Yumi{\rHonorifics - Flashback Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:00.53,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Congratulations, Yumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:02.11,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You did it, Yumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:03.91,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:06.37,Flashback Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}M-My voice is gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:08.70,Flashback Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I-I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:09.96,Flashback Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Help me, Chiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:11.96,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Congrats.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:13.04,Flashback Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:16.34,Flashback Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Chiba... This is no time\Nto be eating a hamburger!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:17.38,Flashback Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:20.15,Flashback Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an8}R-Right... Left... Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.57,0:03:20.84,Flashback Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:22.13,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Takagi{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-kun{\r\be10}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:27.60,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Congratulations,\NTakagi{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-kun{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:31.31,Flashback Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}T-This is all wrong,\NShiratori{\rHonorifics - Flashback Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:33.65,Flashback Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What do I do now?\NAt this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:37.61,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}S-Sato{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-san{\r\be10}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:40.32,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Congratulations...\NTakagi{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-kun{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:46.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.03,0:03:49.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:50.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:52.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It hurt, but I'm so glad\Nit was just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:04:03.53,Signs,,0,0,0,,MPD Detectives' Love Story\NThe Fake Wedding
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:20.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:22.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:26.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was a nice wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:27.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:30.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I wanted\Nto catch the bouquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:33.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez. You're too\Nyoung for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:38.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, are you telling me\Nyou're already engaged to that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:40.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not engaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:43.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'd really love to wear\Na wedding dress sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:53.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could rent you one cheap\Nso you can get a picture taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:54.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:56.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}They're not exactly cheap,\NI don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:58.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I can't go out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:01.52,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine, Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:01.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That voice sounds familiar...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.52,0:05:02.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.86,0:05:05.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:07.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Detective Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:10.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you getting married?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:11.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow, congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:13.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:16.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What a drag. I ran into the people\NI {\i1}least{\i0} want to see right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:18.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, who's the lucky bride?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:21.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly, Dad.\NObviously it's Detective Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:23.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:27.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ta-da! The bride is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:29.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:32.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're Yumi Miyamoto,\Nthe traffic cop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:34.10,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It's... It's not Detective Sato?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.97,0:05:37.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's complicated...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:40.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no, you two\Nmake a perfect pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:42.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shiratori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:43.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:45.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You two should look into\N{\i1}actually{\i0} tying the knot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.94,0:05:48.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah... Should we\Ndo that, darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:49.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:51.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miwako...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:53.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:55.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a target\Non your backs!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:57.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:06:00.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So don't get too\Ncarried away, Yumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:02.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:04.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:06.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have no idea\Nwhat they're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.21,0:06:07.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To tell the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:09.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:13.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A robber wants\Nto kill them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:15.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These... two?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:17.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, they're stand-ins.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:21.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ones who were actually targeted,\Nthe real bride and groom,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:24.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,are the ones\Nwho called us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:29.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Six months ago, a thief in a ski mask\Nraided the home of the bride's family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:33.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The groom managed\Nto chase him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.91,0:06:36.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But as the thief left,\Nhe said...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:39.54,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why, you... You're gonna\Nbe sorry for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:43.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that just the kind of line\Na generic bad guy would drop?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:45.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why go to the effort\Nof stand-ins just for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:49.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it were just an ordinary thief,\Nwe wouldn't do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:53.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the prints on a kitchen knife\Nleft at the crime scene
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:55.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,matched someone\Nwe have on file.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:57.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were the prints\Nof a serial killer
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:07:01.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,who killed six people\Nduring four robberies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:05.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is his MO:\Nwhile the residents were asleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:10.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he would break in,\Nslit their throats with a kitchen knife,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:14.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and after making off\Nwith all the valuables,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.82,0:07:18.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he'd burn the place down and make\Na run for it. It's incredibly brutal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:19.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the night before last,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:22.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a piece of paper was apparently\Ntossed into the bride's mailbox.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:28.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It read, "Congrats on your upcoming wedding.\NI'll give you a big cheer, just you wait."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:30.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:34.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With someone that dangerous,\Nit makes sense to use stand-ins.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:37.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why have Detective Takagi\Nand Yumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} play the parts?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.72,0:07:41.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? You don't think Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}\Nand I are a good match?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:43.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's not\Nwhat I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:45.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It made the most sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:49.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bride, Rei Masudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},\Nand the groom, Masateru Taira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:51.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,look like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.44,0:07:52.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:57.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. They look just like Takagi\Nand the mini patrol car chick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:07:59.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:03.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, is the actual\Nwedding canceled?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:06.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. The groom wanted to hold\Nthe wedding no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:13.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we're going to check everyone\Ncoming into the building for invitations,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:18.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so his only shot will be after the ceremony,\Nduring the rice shower when everyone is leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:21.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's where\Nthese two come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:24.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Obviously, they'll be wearing\Nbulletproof vests, {under their wedding clothes?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:29.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and all the guests will be switched\Nwith police detectives keeping watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:33.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure it's safe?\NYou don't know how the killer will strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:35.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:39.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if it does get out of hand,\NMiwako will swoop in to save us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:40.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:42.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure. But you come\Nafter Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:48.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so cold! Choosing love\Nover friendship? I can't believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:50.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a good reason,\Nyou know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:55.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's more of a chance of the groom\Nincurring the robber's wrath.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:58.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And... Stop clinging to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:59.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miwako!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:04.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I-I'm sorry.\NYou look just like someone I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:09.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must be here for Taira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nand Masudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:12.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NYou too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:13.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:17.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's in wedding hall 3\Nat 5:00 PM, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:19.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll catch you later\Nin the wedding hall, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:22.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:26.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Rei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:30.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wedding hall 3, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:31.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey there, Masudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:35.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's me, Karube.\NThanks for inviting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:37.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think this is the first time\Nwe've met in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:38.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.38,0:09:41.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be looking forward\Nto the big event.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:44.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They've completely mistaken you\Nfor the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:46.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really don't think\Nthey look that similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:49.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It just goes to show\Nwhat a perfect couple these two are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:51.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Shiratori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:09:54.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That would explain why\NI had that dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:57.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we don't want\Nany extra trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:10:01.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and Yumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, you two stay\Nin the waiting room until you're needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:02.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:07.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A lot of people are passing through here,\Nso we should go to a different room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:07.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:13.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll inform the bride and groom\Nabout the current situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:15.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:15.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.05,0:10:16.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse us, then, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:17.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:19.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:21.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Uncle.\NWhy don't you go with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:24.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are a great detective,\Nafter all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:27.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could give\Nthe police a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:29.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,G-Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.64,0:10:32.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right! Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:32.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.11,0:10:32.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:34.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:37.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:38.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:41.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry. You just looked\Nlike someone I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:46.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:48.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you\Ntalking about, Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:51.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We chose this\Nimportant date together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:53.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't say you want\Nto call it off now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:57.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Masateru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},\Nour lives are in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:11:01.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if something happens\Nto everyone who came today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:04.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\NHe'll never show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:06.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:07.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:10.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.18,0:11:11.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.14,0:11:13.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-How's the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:16.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing particularly unusual\Nat present.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:21.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are officers stationed\Nthroughout the building,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.65,0:11:25.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and we'll be by your side\Nat all times, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:27.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, what did I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:30.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way,\Nwho's that behind you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:34.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, him? He's Kogoro Mouri,\Na private detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:36.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He tends to just show up\Nwherever we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:36.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.00,0:11:39.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That famous detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:41.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're Sleeping Kogoro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:43.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Happy to be of service.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:47.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you could\Nfill me in on the details
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:49.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,of that burglary\Nsix months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:51.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:53.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It happened\None snowy night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.56,0:11:55.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was\Npast midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:00.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard a strange sound,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:03.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but when I tried to turn on the lights,\Nnothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:07.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought something was strange\Nand walked toward the sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.91,0:12:15.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A man noticed me\Nand came after me with a kitchen knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:21.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was running away\Nfrantically in the darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:24.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he caught me\Nat the front entrance,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:26.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and when death\Nstared me in the face,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:30.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he came from the front entrance\Nand saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:34.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had a bad feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:37.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her parents had gone on a trip\Nwith the servants that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:41.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the house was empty\Napart from her and an elderly servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:44.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he fought the man off...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:46.66,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Call the police! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:49.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...while I ran back to my room\Nto call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:55.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I got back, the burglar was running away.\NThat's when he yelled that at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:13:02.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when he said\N"You're gonna be sorry for this", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:02.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:05.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe\Nyou two were unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.34,0:13:09.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did get a bit\Nscratched up,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:10.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but his left hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.81,0:13:14.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While struggling with the thief,\Nmy hand must have landed wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:17.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because I broke my wrist\Nand my thumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:20.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My arm was in a sling\Nuntil last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:24.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if I'd known\Nthat would happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:26.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd have liked to have moved\Nafter he got better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:27.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moved?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:30.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her father thinks that if a man this dangerous is after her,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:33.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she should leave Japan\Nafter the wedding,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:37.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so he bought us\Na cottage in Hawaii.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:40.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That sounds nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:43.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cottage has good security,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:47.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so we wouldn't have to worry about\Nsomeone breaking in like the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:50.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like the other day...\NYou had another break-in?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:52.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:54.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time,\Nit was at his apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:57.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I had taken her out, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:13:59.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was anything stolen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:01.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:03.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But my PC, which I had shut off,\Nwas turned on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:07.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:10.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, Megure here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:12.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Chiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.78,0:14:16.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! A burnt corpse\Nwith its throat slit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:17.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.91,0:14:19.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In an abandoned warehouse\Nby the Teimuzu River.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.17,0:14:23.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a man\Nin his 30s or 40s.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:25.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's wearing a dark suit\Nwith a white tie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:28.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And according to the forensic\Nreport I just received,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:31.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,on the nails of the burnt left hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:35.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They found the prints\Nof the serial robber-killer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.97,0:14:39.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A white tie\Nmeans formal dress...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:44.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, did you have a list of\Nthe wedding guests on that PC?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:48.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. We planned the wedding\Ntogether at his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:52.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the body belongs to one\Nof the people on that list.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:54.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man was murdered\Nfor his wedding invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.03,0:14:59.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Does that mean that he's already\Nhere in the wedding hall?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:07.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call it off! Call it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:14.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cancel all the weddings and evacuate all\Nthe people from the wedding hall, on the double!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:19.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The serial robber-killer might be hiding\Nsomewhere in the building,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:22.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I can't allow any innocent\Ncivilians to remain inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:23.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:25.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please wait a second,\NMr. Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:30.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no real proof that\Nthat scumbag's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:34.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you think you can ruin our\Nand everyone else's important day?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:36.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Taira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:38.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Six months ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.69,0:15:42.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you fought off a robber who broke into\Nyour bride Rei Masudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:44.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He might hold\Na grudge against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:45.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:49.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there is the threatening letter that was\Nin her mailbox two days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:53.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's also the charred body we found in an empty warehouse by the Teimuzu River today,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:56.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,with its throat slit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:58.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The MO is the same as the robber's,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:16:02.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and we found his prints on the nails of\Nthe left hand of the charred body's remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:05.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The body was dressed\Nin formal attire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:08.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention yesterday,\Nwhen someone broke into your apartment,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.44,0:16:12.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and turned on your PC,\Nwhich you had shut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:19.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely the robber-killer got into your PC\Nand got the list of wedding guests,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:24.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,contacted one of the people on the list,\Nkilled him, stole his invitation,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:28.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and then entered\Nthe wedding hall in his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.76,0:16:30.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a high probability\Nof that being the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:35.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right. And all for the sole\Npurpose of revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:39.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we still don't have any proof\Nthat the victim is one of our guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:43.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:47.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've received a gift for\Nthe bride and the groom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.10,0:16:49.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They've been asked\Nto open it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:52.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:54.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's it from?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.15,0:16:55.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.11,0:16:59.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just passed along\Nfrom the staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:03.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, geez! You brought a suspicious\Npackage straight into this room?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:06.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:10.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I checked inside first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:12.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:14.82,Signs,,0,0,0,,Call me once you've\Nchecked this ♥ - Shimizu
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:14.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's from Shimizu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.17,0:17:16.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, one of our friends\Nfrom the chat room...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:19.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's that video, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:20.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Friend from the chat room?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:25.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, the two of us frequent\Na website about hot springs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:31.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We invited the site's members to\Na party tonight after the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.44,0:17:33.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're going to play\Nthis video at the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:37.32,Signs,,0,0,0,,Call me once you've\Nchecked this ♥ - Shimizu
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:37.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she wants us to\Ncheck it out beforehand,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.03,0:17:39.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she must have finally\Nfinished editing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.32,0:17:41.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May we take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:45.41,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A day in the dating life of\NTaira{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-san{\r\be10} and Rei{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-chan{\r\be10}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:47.83,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Let's take a peek at a romantic day\Nin the life of our couple,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:53.71,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}who deepened their bond by finally getting\Nengaged after chasing off a burglar last month!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.21,0:17:56.92,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh? No way,\Nyou're already here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:17:57.33,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:17:58.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:00.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The entrance to my apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:01.97,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Let me get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:02.85,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:05.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did this Shimizu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} person\Nrecord this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:06.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.14,0:18:09.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She lives nearby, so we've become\Ngood friends in real life too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:12.11,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:15.69,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We're going to\NTropical Land today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:16.11,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:18.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You left your keys on\Nthe light in the entryway?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:20.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you usually\Nkeep your key there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.61,0:18:22.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, force of habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:27.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means this Shimizu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} knows\Nhow to get into his apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:30.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's not that\Nkind of person!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:34.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's the one who kept telling us we needed\Nto talk to the police about the break-in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:36.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kept telling you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.67,0:18:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean you never told the police\Nabout the break-in?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:43.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right. After all,\Nnothing was stolen...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:50.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But just in case, we postponed the wedding\None day from the data on the PC,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:52.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so even if the robber\Nmanaged to get in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.97,0:18:55.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he wouldn't\Nmake it to the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.07,0:19:00.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if you kept the invitees' names\Nand addresses on the PC,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:02.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he could just pretend to be\Nan acquaintance of yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:07.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,get in touch with\Nsomeone on the list,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.33,0:19:08.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and get the real date\Nfrom them, couldn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:10.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:15.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't the bride and the groom meet\Nthe people who came to the wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:20.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That bad guy's pretending to be\Nsomeone the two of them know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:22.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:25.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meet them? If they did that,\Nthey could get attacked...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:28.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, they don't need to\Nmeet them face-to-face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.06,0:19:32.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They could just check from\Na room next to the lobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:36.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the current situation,\Nwhy don't we try that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:42.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we get clumsy by shutting down the wedding,\Nthe robber might do something desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.15,0:19:42.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:46.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, can you help us match\Nthe names and faces of your guests?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.12,0:19:47.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.74,0:19:48.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.12,0:19:52.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, go talk to\NTakagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and Yumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:56.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The robber may be\Nin the building right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:20:00.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're standing in for the bride and groom, so you could also be attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.84,0:20:02.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:03.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:05.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:08.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you get there,\Nstay with them and keep watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:09.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:13.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm scared, Masateru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:15.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine.\NI'm here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:22.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Atsuko,\Ncheck it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:25.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look!\NAren't I pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:28.33,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh, Yumi?!\NYou're getting married?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:30.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly!\NOf course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:33.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just police work.\NW-o-r-k.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:34.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er, Yumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:37.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think you should be\Nleaking that to an outsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:40.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!\NI'm well aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.25,0:20:41.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you butt out\Nof my phone call?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:43.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.97,0:20:47.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that man's voice just now?\NNah, it's just the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:51.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Geez. She was all over me\Njust a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:53.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I just don't get women.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:56.81,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ta-da! The bride is me!{XREF: 5:33}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:21:00.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Anyway, why did I\Nhave such a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.23,0:21:02.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Even if I did have to act as\Na decoy with Yumi{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10},
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.47,0:21:03.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}that doesn't mean we had\Nto go through the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.99,0:21:05.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's a premonition.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.41,0:21:12.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got a repressed wish in your heart\Nthat says you want to marry Kitada.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.16,0:21:15.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NI can't stand Kitada.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:19.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know what they say,\Na lie is a half-truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.08,0:21:22.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You and Kitada are\Ndestined for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:26.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A premonition?\NA repressed wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:27.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:30.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.97,0:21:32.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's not true, is it?\NAbout premonitions in dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way a repressed wish\Nwould go from a lie to a truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:37.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.90,0:21:40.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about,\NTakagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.15,0:21:41.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you shouldn't be out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.56,0:21:43.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't the Inspector say\Nto stay back in the lobby?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.73,0:21:44.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.53,0:21:47.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? What's\Nnot possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:49.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay out of other\Npeople's conversations!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.74,0:21:50.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.95,0:21:52.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go,\NSato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.83,0:21:54.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold still!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.62,0:21:58.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez. What a time\Nto break one's arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.83,0:21:59.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.75,0:22:04.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on with\Nthat couple?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.59,0:22:06.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.60,0:22:15.58,Signs,,0,0,0,,Masudo Family
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.34,0:22:31.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How does it look?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:34.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.67,0:22:39.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you see anyone\Nyou don't recognize?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.42,0:22:43.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.08,0:22:45.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.30,0:22:47.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's some people\NI don't recognize,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.46,0:22:51.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,like that man in sunglasses\Nwith the tan and light hair,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.30,0:22:53.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.36,0:22:56.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the tall man\Nwith the kappa head,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.93,0:22:58.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.26,0:23:01.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that man with the beard\Nand glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.20,0:23:03.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That makes three people.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.69,0:23:07.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think the third man\Nis the most suspicious one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.24,0:23:10.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? W-Why do you\Nthink that, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.26,0:23:12.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.60,0:23:14.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's been taking photos\Nof all the bridal couples,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.53,0:23:17.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,claiming to mistake them\Nfor someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.17,0:23:20.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case,\Nhe might be...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.52,0:23:22.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the photographer,\NUncle Gunji.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.12,0:23:27.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you don't\Nrecognize him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.00,0:23:29.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.74,0:23:33.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen him\Nsince I was little,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.12,0:23:36.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and back then, he was skinny\Nand didn't have a beard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.89,0:23:41.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Over the years, he's flown around\Nthe world as a photographer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.00,0:23:42.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen him\Nat all in that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.94,0:23:45.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about\Nthe other two?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.80,0:23:49.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't like the look\Nof that creep with the shades.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.96,0:23:51.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He might be...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.26,0:23:54.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That might be the snowboarding\Ninstructor, Shimabukuro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.71,0:23:57.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,who I took some lessons from\Nsome time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.34,0:24:02.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I invited him to the wedding because\NMasateru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and I met in his class.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.89,0:24:05.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.09,0:24:08.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I don't\Nsnowboard anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.13,0:24:13.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't recognize him because his face was always hidden behind a hat and goggles.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.57,0:24:17.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.21,0:24:20.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the man\Nwith the kappa head?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.99,0:24:28.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only person I can think of is Karube{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},\Nthe webmaster of the hot springs forums.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.02,0:24:30.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hot springs forums?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.75,0:24:32.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Webmaster...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.87,0:24:33.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.98,0:24:36.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means the person\Nwho runs the website.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.20,0:24:39.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I k-knew that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.94,0:24:43.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's very shy and has never been\Nto any of our offline meet-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.45,0:24:47.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had to persuade him\Nto attend our wedding,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.42,0:24:49.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so today's the first time I saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.50,0:24:53.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he knew\Nwhat {\i1}you{\i0} looked like,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.44,0:24:56.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,since he called out\Nto Yumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.69,0:25:00.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I sent him an end-of-summer greeting card\Nyesterday with my picture on it
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.34,0:25:02.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so he'd know\Nwhat I look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.72,0:25:05.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.19,0:25:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like we'll have to\Ncall in the three of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.00,0:25:11.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,run their prints and\Ncompare them to the robber.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.56,0:25:13.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.28,0:25:15.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That would be\Nrude to our guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.90,0:25:19.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we're out of options.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.30,0:25:23.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say. How did you know the prints\Nbelonged to the bad guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.85,0:25:29.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We got a print from one\Nof the four scenes
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.53,0:25:33.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,of the murders he committed\Nbefore breaking into Rei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s house.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.74,0:25:37.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was found on\Na victim's earring.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.15,0:25:41.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We also found fabric from a cotton glove\Nstuck between the victim's teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.45,0:25:44.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The burglar must have tried to gag the victim\Nwith his left hand before slitting her throat,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.96,0:25:47.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but she struggled\Nand pulled the glove off,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.50,0:25:51.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so he covered her mouth with his bare hand,\Ntouching her earring in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.74,0:25:57.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The same print was found on the kitchen knife\Nthe thief left behind at Rei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s house.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.89,0:26:01.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We also found a left-hand\Npalm print on the knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.54,0:26:05.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how we know the fingerprint on the earring came from the thief's left ring finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.69,0:26:10.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, Inspector, he wasn't wearing\Ngloves during the robbery?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.91,0:26:11.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.77,0:26:13.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it looks like he was wearing gloves,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.50,0:26:16.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so the prints must have been from handling the knife beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.80,0:26:21.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the four previous cases, the killer took\Nthe weapon with him after the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.24,0:26:24.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must have touched the knife at some point\Nand didn't bother wiping his prints
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.86,0:26:26.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because he didn't expect to be\Nsurprised by Taira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.80,0:26:30.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, we didn't find his prints anywhere\Nin the house, except that knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.18,0:26:34.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Taira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},\Nwas the front door locked
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.19,0:26:36.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when you rushed in\Nto save her?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.84,0:26:38.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it was open.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.65,0:26:40.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.47,0:26:45.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I managed to run for the door by\Ngroping around in the pitch-darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.95,0:26:47.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and had just\Nopened the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.87,0:26:52.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is anything wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.45,0:26:54.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I just thought\NI saw something then...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.75,0:26:56.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.19,0:26:57.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Try to remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.59,0:26:58.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.74,0:27:00.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will you stop\Ninterrogating her?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.25,0:27:01.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.22,0:27:02.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.55,0:27:04.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.70,0:27:06.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at those three...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.93,0:27:11.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The kappa guy has a bandage\Nwrapped around his left ring finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.88,0:27:14.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bearded man\Nin the glasses
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.17,0:27:16.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,has a band-aid\Non his left ring finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.05,0:27:21.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it looks like the guy in shades\Nis keeping his left hand in his pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.52,0:27:26.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Almost like they don't want to get prints\Nfrom their left ring finger on anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.56,0:27:28.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.95,0:27:32.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ask those three\Nfor their fingerprints!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.19,0:27:35.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That should make it clear\Nthat the robber isn't here!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.93,0:27:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,None of the people {\i1}I{\i0} invited\Nare suspicious people!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.98,0:27:44.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it looks like Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s\Nalready talking to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.91,0:27:49.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That brat's taking things into\Nhis own hands {\i1}again{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.22,0:27:53.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.60,0:27:58.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what's up\Nwith their left hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.60,0:28:02.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man with the tied bandage\Nsprained it playing sandlot baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.46,0:28:05.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man with the band-aid\Njammed his finger in the door at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.88,0:28:08.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the guy with his hand in his pocket\Nsaid it was just a habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.98,0:28:11.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, and he's wearing\Nsunglasses indoors
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.82,0:28:14.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because he has\Na stye on his eyelid.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.33,0:28:16.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's it! Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.71,0:28:20.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Masateru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.46,0:28:23.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Masateru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} rushed\Nto save me, I saw it...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.98,0:28:25.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.36,0:28:27.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a stye\Non the robber's right eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.44,0:28:31.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.32,0:28:34.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-A stye?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.10,0:28:38.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the robber is\Nthe man in sunglasses?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.74,0:28:41.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But doesn't it only\Ntake a week for a stye...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.48,0:28:56.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A stye...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.92,0:28:58.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That clears it all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.60,0:29:01.28,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The identity of the serial\Nrobber-killer...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.23,0:29:13.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-The robber might\Nalready have snuck in?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.50,0:29:15.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Into this wedding hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.32,0:29:16.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.48,0:29:19.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like he tracked down\None of the guests
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.50,0:29:22.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and killed him\Nto steal his invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.07,0:29:29.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means you two, the decoys for the\Nbride and groom, need to be extra careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.68,0:29:31.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there's\Nanother possibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.34,0:29:33.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Another?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.32,0:29:34.75,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Oh, and Yumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.25,0:29:34.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, another?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.47,0:29:37.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got a favour\Nto ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.02,0:29:38.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.84,0:29:42.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to ask, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r},\Nbut could you leave us alone for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.61,0:29:45.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is girl talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.06,0:29:47.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.46,0:29:51.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll just go to the boys' room...\NWait, where {\i1}was{\i0} the boys' room?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.10,0:29:52.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be back in a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.65,0:30:07.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course!\NI figured you were gonna ask,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.78,0:30:09.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I made sure\Nto bring some along.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.75,0:30:10.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.53,0:30:13.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry about this, Yumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.51,0:30:26.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We won't be able to tell who the robber is\Njust by looking at their faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.44,0:30:32.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't we get the prints of the three people\NRei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the bride, didn't recognize,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.20,0:30:35.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and compare them with\Nthe robber's prints?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.00,0:30:38.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, you mustn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.11,0:30:40.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if you're wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.90,0:30:44.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the only clue we have\Nother than the robber's prints
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.63,0:30:48.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is the stye\Non the robber's right eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.84,0:30:53.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that was six months ago.\NIt should have healed by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.80,0:30:56.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you recognize the robber\Nfrom his voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.79,0:31:00.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He did drop that line,\N"You're gonna be sorry for this", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.64,0:31:01.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.48,0:31:04.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he was wearing a ski mask,\Nso his voice was muffled.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.74,0:31:06.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, if we had noticed anything\Nspecial about his voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.75,0:31:08.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we would've told the police\Nsix months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.72,0:31:13.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector. The staff would like\Nto start the wedding soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.16,0:31:15.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.26,0:31:16.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's get the\Nceremony started.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.17,0:31:16.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.82,0:31:18.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.99,0:31:19.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.73,0:31:21.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.10,0:31:21.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.58,0:31:29.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.17,0:31:30.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.29,0:31:34.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's go through with\Nthe wedding as planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.48,0:31:37.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're so worried,\Nwhy don't you just mix with the guests
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.64,0:31:39.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and keep a lookout there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.14,0:31:43.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure\Nhe won't show up!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.21,0:31:44.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wait! Taira{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.49,0:31:51.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let him go.\NHe wants his big day, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.76,0:31:53.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let him go through\Nwith it? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.05,0:31:58.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, once I've told you\Nmy deductions,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.26,0:31:59.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.51,0:32:03.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The choice will be yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.43,0:32:18.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Huh? Oh, geez, there's nobody\Nstanding outside the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.38,0:32:23.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Takagi!\NMay I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.60,0:32:27.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm coming in...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.48,0:32:30.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.50,0:32:33.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-There's nobody here...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.22,0:32:34.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.97,0:32:36.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, there you are, Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.90,0:32:40.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure called\Njust a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.63,0:32:44.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said you're to stay in this room\Nand await further orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.40,0:32:46.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"You're"...\NWhat about Yumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.86,0:32:47.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.77,0:32:50.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the Inspector contacted her too.\NShe's gone out.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.79,0:32:52.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.29,0:32:54.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh... Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.35,0:32:59.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In a moment the bride, Rei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},\Nwill enter, escorted by her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.46,0:33:02.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please greet them with\Na round of applause.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.98,0:33:17.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.23,0:33:23.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been six months,\Nhasn't it, you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.93,0:33:24.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.93,0:33:27.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Catch that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.41,0:33:27.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.98,0:33:30.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah-ah-ah,\Ndon't try anything funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.06,0:33:33.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know there's\Nplenty of cops here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.94,0:33:35.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.30,0:33:38.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be out of here as soon\Nas I've sliced these two to ribbons.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.48,0:33:42.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough\Nof your bad acting...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.27,0:33:45.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.04,0:33:46.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,G-Get real...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.56,0:33:49.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the guy who broke into\Nthat woman's house six months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.04,0:33:54.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If this is supposed to be a joke,\Nyou should give up before it stops being funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.29,0:33:58.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way\Nyou're the robber.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.86,0:34:03.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? And how do\Nyou know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.24,0:34:05.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did you know\Nhe wasn't the robber?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.55,0:34:07.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er, well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.89,0:34:15.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you rushed into Rei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s house to save her six months ago, it was pitch black inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.79,0:34:18.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I find it hard to believe\Nyou'd recognize him solely from his build.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.43,0:34:20.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It was his voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.45,0:34:25.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? But you said you didn't remember\Nanything about the robber's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.13,0:34:30.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw a police detective earlier\Nwith the same voice as that masked man.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.46,0:34:33.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And where was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.09,0:34:38.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't remember, but it had to have been\Nsomewhere in this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.31,0:34:43.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know anyone who'd\Nplay such a lame joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.93,0:34:47.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right. This man is a detective\Nwho works under me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.04,0:34:50.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.71,0:34:55.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He only just got here from the\Nwarehouse by the Teimuzu River.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.97,0:34:57.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Chiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.04,0:34:59.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.53,0:35:03.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So let me\Nask you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.49,0:35:06.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did you know\Nhe wasn't the robber?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.37,0:35:08.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er, well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.09,0:35:13.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm also curious about why you opened that\Nunlabelled package without hesitation
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.78,0:35:16.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when it was delivered\Nto your waiting room.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.34,0:35:22.05,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No sensible man in your situation\Nwould open a strange package
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.38,0:35:26.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,without checking carefully first,\Nunless, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.76,0:35:27.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.68,0:35:32.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You already knew nothing dangerous would be\Ncoming, and that person would not show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.54,0:35:34.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were certain of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.55,0:35:38.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And no surprise\Nthat you thought that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.53,0:35:40.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.07,0:35:46.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd already killed them in the warehouse near the Teimuzu River.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.17,0:35:51.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The robber-killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.07,0:36:00.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could someone explain\Nwhat's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.38,0:36:03.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why am I\Nthe only one here?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.06,0:36:05.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I said,\Nwe're really busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.71,0:36:10.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At least let me in on\Nwhere Yumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} went!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.18,0:36:14.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought Sato was guarding you\Nin the waiting room.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.38,0:36:15.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-Nope...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.80,0:36:16.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.52,0:36:19.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I knew what was going on,\NI wouldn't be asking...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.67,0:36:25.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, this is no time\Nto fool around with me, Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sa{\r}—
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.43,0:36:29.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I killed the robber?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.86,0:36:33.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just thought the robber\Nwould never show his face
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.71,0:36:37.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,with a bunch\Nof cops around.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.28,0:36:40.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would you assume I killed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.05,0:36:43.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, shouldn't you check out\Nthose three suspicious guests first,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.42,0:36:46.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,before you start suspecting—
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.72,0:36:47.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.44,0:36:48.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.42,0:36:54.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All three of them mistook Yumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r},\Nthe decoy, for the bride and spoke to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.46,0:36:58.23,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, I-I'm sorry.\NYou look just like someone I know.{XREF 9:09}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.63,0:37:00.73,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey there, Masudo{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-san{\r\be10}!{XREF 9:39}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.02,0:37:01.43,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yo.{XREF 9:31}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.76,0:37:07.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If one of them\Nhad been the killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.86,0:37:10.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he would have\Navoided the bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.70,0:37:11.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.56,0:37:16.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, he wouldn't know much about\Nthe guest's relationship with the bride,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.04,0:37:18.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so talking to her\Nwould be risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.91,0:37:21.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what if she recognized the voice\Nfrom when he broke in?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.69,0:37:25.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even the robber himself\Ncouldn't be certain
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.48,0:37:28.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,whether or not\Nshe would recognize him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.50,0:37:35.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we didn't notice that detail\Nuntil Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} pointed it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.80,0:37:38.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then what about\Ntheir left ring fingers?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.15,0:37:40.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't all three of them\Nhiding them?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.50,0:37:42.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was sheer\Ncoincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.80,0:37:45.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's say one of the three\Nwas the robber.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.65,0:37:50.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He left the print\Nwhen his glove came off
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.74,0:37:53.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,while he was struggling\Nwith one of his victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.75,0:37:58.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's unlikely that he'd know\Nwhich finger left a print.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.54,0:38:00.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'd want to hide\Nhis entire hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.64,0:38:02.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you,\Non the other hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.71,0:38:06.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,managed to hear about the prints\Nfrom the police after the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.97,0:38:10.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you pretended to break\Nyour left thumb and wrist
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.38,0:38:13.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and were wearing\Na cast, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.65,0:38:16.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were trying\Nto hide your prints.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.11,0:38:20.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As it turns out,\Nthe prints on the knife
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.67,0:38:24.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,were {\i1}your{\i0} prints,\Nfrom when you fought with the robber.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.97,0:38:29.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We only found prints\Nfrom your left hand
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.22,0:38:31.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because you were holding\Nsomething in your right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.28,0:38:34.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember what\NRei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.24,0:38:38.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She had to grope around in the dark\Nto find the front entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.08,0:38:44.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But after you ran in,\Nshe noticed a stye on the robber's eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.74,0:38:48.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason she saw that the robber\Nhad a stye in the pitch darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.97,0:38:52.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was because when you came to help her,\Nyou were holding a flashlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.72,0:38:55.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.26,0:39:01.48,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Before the fiancé came to save her, he already\Nknew the power had been cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.87,0:39:04.48,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That is to say, he and the robber\Nwere in cahoots.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.94,0:39:12.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lucky for you, when you burst in\Nand wrestled the robber to the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.57,0:39:15.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,your prints only got\Non the knife,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.86,0:39:20.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so we assumed they belonged\Nto the other man.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.73,0:39:23.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason you betrayed your partner\Nand saved Rei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.47,0:39:25.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was because while you were\Nplanning your attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.57,0:39:29.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you developed feelings for her...\Nam I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.57,0:39:32.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your betrayed partner\Ndropped that line on you
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.92,0:39:35.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and sought an opportunity\Nfor revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.66,0:39:38.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what happened is:\NYou let him break into your home,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.80,0:39:42.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,get into your computer and see the data there\Nbefore you changed the date to today,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.61,0:39:44.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,giving him the wrong impression\Nthat the ceremony was yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.99,0:39:45.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.88,0:39:50.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he showed up at a wedding hall in formal attire and waited for you to show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.36,0:39:52.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You gave him\Nsome excuse,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.68,0:39:56.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,lured him to the empty warehouse\Nby the Teimuzu River,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.03,0:39:58.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.79,0:40:01.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Except that I didn't\Nhave feelings for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.70,0:40:06.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason I saved her was that I could\Nget richer by marrying her than killing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.59,0:40:07.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could you say\Nsuch a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.96,0:40:11.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I tried explaining the new plan to my partner,\Nbut he just didn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.28,0:40:14.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally, he was such a pain\Nthat I had to get rid of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.82,0:40:18.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was a brainless idiot who never knew\Nhow to do anything more than crack a safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.21,0:40:21.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.15,0:40:22.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like you cops!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.56,0:40:35.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think you can show off a weapon like that\Nin front of a serial robber-killer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.69,0:40:36.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.30,0:40:38.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.28,0:40:44.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no use! Everyone here, except\Nthe father of the bride, is a cop!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.60,0:40:45.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.85,0:40:46.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get away?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.32,0:40:50.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once you have my prints,\Nit's all over for me anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.67,0:40:51.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.42,0:40:53.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm giving a gift to Hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.09,0:40:55.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As many of you\Nas I can take with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.31,0:40:59.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.03,0:41:03.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.20,0:41:06.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.23,0:41:09.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.79,0:41:12.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Too bad!\NStill not Miwako.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.55,0:41:16.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't those Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.84,0:41:17.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.65,0:41:20.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We switched places! She borrowed my hair gel\Nto make her hair look like mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.59,0:41:22.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You switched places?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.77,0:41:26.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I tried to make Miwako jealous\Nby hanging all over you
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.54,0:41:30.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so she'd want to put on\Nthat wedding dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.75,0:41:34.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't easy for her\Nto be your bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.35,0:41:39.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her abs were too big\Nfor the protective vest.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.52,0:41:41.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So where's Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.11,0:41:46.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the Inspector told her to come\Nto the wedding hall, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.73,0:41:47.71,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Y-Yumi{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-kun{\r\be10}!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.32,0:42:01.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One down.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.07,0:42:05.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't...!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.48,0:42:11.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.13,0:42:15.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wires in a corset\Nare pretty tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.60,0:42:17.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miwako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.49,0:42:18.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.32,0:42:24.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.88,0:42:32.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.83,0:42:33.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.77,0:42:35.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I can't grab him properly in this dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.46,0:42:40.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.70,0:42:43.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}R-Right, normal shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.51,0:42:45.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Out of the way,\Nbrat!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.47,0:42:46.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.25,0:42:47.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.14,0:43:02.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.51,0:43:03.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.15,0:43:04.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.82,0:43:08.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.63,0:43:15.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.52,0:43:18.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.75,0:43:20.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.13,0:43:23.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.02,0:43:27.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I got it!\NThis is the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.06,0:43:29.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?!\NWhy were you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.85,0:43:32.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask you\Nthe same question...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.06,0:43:40.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing there,\NTakagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.80,0:43:54.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ran and Detective Sato\Ncan be pretty scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.69,0:45:26.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you had suspicions\Nabout the groom all along?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.82,0:45:27.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.87,0:45:32.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sometime afterwards, I noticed something\Nfunny in that video in the waiting room.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.25,0:45:34.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Despite broken bones,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.62,0:45:37.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he managed to change quickly\Ninto a zippered jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.71,0:45:42.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suspected his cast was a fake\Ndesigned to hide his left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.17,0:45:44.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plus, he didn't report\Nthe break-in.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.30,0:45:47.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. If the police were\Nto search his apartment,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.84,0:45:51.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they'd recognize\Nhis fingerprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.64,0:45:56.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once I put the pieces together, I couldn't\Nallow anyone near such a dangerous man.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.10,0:45:59.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I switched\Nplaces with Yumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.48,0:46:04.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't seem to mind\Nwearing that wedding dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.07,0:46:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.45,0:46:08.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't look good\Nin that foofy stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.53,0:46:09.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.70,0:46:12.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But one other thing\Nsurprised me...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.49,0:46:15.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy with the camera\Nwas a famous photographer
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.79,0:46:17.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,who was there to create\Nan ad for the wedding hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.68,0:46:29.68,Signs,,0,0,0,,The bride takes charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.51,0:46:24.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.63,0:46:26.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move it!\NThis is so embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.76,0:46:27.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.97,0:46:29.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yumi!\NHey, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.43,0:46:31.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C'mon, c'mon...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.35,0:46:34.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If just that dream were\Nto come true, it would be nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.68,0:46:37.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Izawa, Yamamoto, Murakoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.98,0:46:39.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've still got\Nthose three to question.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.52,0:46:51.99,Signs,,0,0,0,,The bride takes charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.77,0:46:45.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tear it down and I'll have to take you\Nin for property damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.07,0:46:46.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.40,0:46:48.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking\Nabout, Chiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.79,0:46:55.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, this is incredible!{1:53}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.20,0:46:59.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's as if the ghosts you love so much are about to come out of the poster.{1:57}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.42,0:47:02.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wants to kill you?{NO MATCH, but influenced by 4:05}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.52,0:47:09.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, wasn't that the signal?{14:30}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.34,0:47:10.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw it, too!{14:33}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.59,0:47:11.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!{14:38}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.10,0:47:22.06,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:\NTrick vs. Magic\N(Part 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.35,0:47:26.99,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint:\NStage Lighting
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.99,0:47:29.13,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Say. Which one was the next wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.13,0:47:29.70,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.70,0:47:30.57,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Trick or magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.57,0:47:32.12,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding.
